metadata.name: Metheors #2007
metadata.description: MΞTHΞORS is an art-focused and philanthropic project centered around the conflict of 4 warring MetaVerse factions; Alpha, Sigma, Gamma, and Omega. Each NFT from this original collection is a unique creation by highly-regarded 3D Artist Diego Zanelli, who has a background in video game and jewelry design. All 2112 pieces of this collection are designed and crafted by hand, without the use of randomization algorithms.
